column6: Point locations of Pennsylvania Game Commission public shooting ranges. Rangetype 'R' = Rifle, 'P' = Pistol. Shooting permits or valid Pennsylvania hunting license required in order to use these facilities. Information available on the PGC website and Hunting Digest. Be sure to check the status of the range to ensure that it is open.
